longBusinessSummary: Dynamic Cables Limited manufactures and supplies cables and conductors in India and internationally. The company offers bare and insulated conductors; 66KV power cables; MV and LV aerial bunched, and power copper and aluminum cables; LV control and concentric cables; railway signaling cables; galvanized stay and earth wires; and instrumentation cables. It serves government and private utility and distribution companies, EPC contractors, industrial sectors, solar projects, and railway systems. The company was formerly known as Dynamic Engineers. Dynamic Cables Limited was founded in 1986 and is based in Jaipur, India.
